":"a71ef45b468a61bdaaac3231a66784dd9b5a8a0c","tid":2104362,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T01:54:33.000Z","msg":"水警上周一（6日）在果州群島東北面追截走私船隻時，被走私船撞向小艇，<span class=\"red\"><strong>一名水警手指嚴重受傷，右手食指兩節需要截肢</strong></span>，警方拘捕一人，並檢獲約26萬元走私物品，<span class=\"red\"><strong>惟警方一直未有對外公布，至昨日警方才回應本報查詢證實事件。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n本報早前收到消息，周三（8日）向警方查詢，警方昨日回應指，水警小艇分區人員上周一晚上約10時半在果州群島東北面海面發現一艘可疑船隻，水警立即前往追截。該可疑船隻拒絕聽從警方發出的停船國際信號及指示，更撞向水警小艇。水警其後拘捕一名本地男子涉嫌「危害他人海上安全」及「企圖輸出未列艙單貨物」，並檢獲約40部舊電話及50件化裝品，市值約26.8萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，行動中一名警務人員被該可疑船隻撞傷手指，清醒被送往東區醫院治理，翌日出院。據了解，該名水警手指嚴重受傷，右手食指兩節需要截肢。<br />\n<br />\n水警：購新小艇 疑部署訓練不足肇禍<br />\n<br />\n據了解，水警高層高度重視事件，並向同僚發放信息，提醒海上高速追截及攔截是水警最為高風險之工種，未有相關訓練、經驗、保護裝備、同等級之船種、足夠支援等，絕不可進行高速追截及攔截行動。有水警向本報指，水警近日從美國購入新小艇，質疑是否相關部署或訓練不足，或有人為疏忽，導致意外。<span class=\"red\"><strong>該水警又關注，美國對香港有制裁行動，或影響日後小艇的保養，質疑為何仍要購入，又關注受傷警員日後或無法開槍，影響執勤。</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200712/s00002/1594491217575/%E8%BF%BD%E6%88%AA%E8%B5%B0%E7%A7%81%E8%88%B9%E8%A2%AB%E6%92%9E-%E6%B0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%82%B7%E9%A3%9F%E6%8C%87%E9%9C%80%E6%88%AA%E8%82%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200712%2Fs00002%2F1594491217575%2F%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%2588%25AA%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E7%25A7%2581%25E8%2588%25B9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2592%259E-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2582%25B7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%2588%25AA%25E8%2582%25A2&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=3a9ec0af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200712%2Fs00002%2F1594491217575%2F%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%2588%25AA%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E7%25A7%2581%25E8%2588%25B9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2592%259E-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2582%25B7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%2588%25AA%25E8%2582%25A2&h=40d9b959\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200712/s00002/1594491217575/%E8%BF%BD%E6%88%AA%E8%B5%B0%E7%A7%81%E8%88%B9%E8%A2%AB%E6%92%9E-%E6%B0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%82%B7%E9%A3%9F%E6%8C%87%E9%9C%80%E6%88%AA%E8%82%A2</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"佢老婆一定係林嘉欣咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bdf4f8c8d43b9a2d15b99ff73f54aa90aa712c","tid":2104362,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bca7c3edfe383309774ec5dcf522520b56840c6","tid":2104362,"uid":237562,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:11:42.000Z","msg":"死差佬當時唔出現喺嗰個地方咪冇嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728158/page/1\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4b14N8p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4b14N8p.png&h=5a039ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bj6g0P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bj6g0P.png&h=dbad9b97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09e93cad122bf8d7579d37b2d9b2e328beadeff1","tid":2104362,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b654b1d7d9d08e8b0c08cb95d99f27d33d04006c","tid":2104362,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1dd6c84ec01adbe95496db3aea4d3bfa4dcca9","tid":2104362,"uid":101650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"大家記住<br />\n水狗係防暴隊入面打人打得最落力嗰班"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"沒錯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢班水軍 要小心<br />\n大陸經濟衰退 多人走私 隨時船都撞沉同炸沉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces